<div class="content-group1">
  <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/doem0zjpf/image/upload/v1562844774/WOOO_u2b6qt.png" alt="">
  <div class="flex-left">

    <h3 class="">Beat Procrastination and Achieve Your Goals!</h3>
    <div class="paragraph-height">
      <p class="paragraph-margin">Being productive can sometimes be a daunting task. But it doesn't have to be. With Conquered Time, you can find clarity and finally enjoy the process of self-improvement!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content-group2">
  <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/doem0zjpf/image/upload/v1562845299/WAPE_ncmzvw.png" alt="">
