    <h3 class="">Create A Tactical Journal</h3>
    <div class="paragraph-height">
      <p class="paragraph-margin">We usually procrastinate when our goals are too big or difficult to achive. So you first need to break down your large goals into small and managable milestones.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content-group3">
  <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/doem0zjpf/image/upload/v1562845793/LASSE_KRONER_qrhdxn.png" alt="">
  <div class="flex-left">
    <h3>Begin Your Focus Timer</h3>
    <div class="paragraph-height">
      <p class=" paragraph-margin">Once you've made your tactical journal, select any one of your chosen milestone and initiate your focus timer. During this timer stay away from all distractions and work with complete devotion and present moment
        mindfulness. It's all about quality over quantity!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="full-height">
<div class="content-group5">
  <div class="banner-main">
    <h3>Start Your Journey</h3>
    <div class="image-wrap">
    <img class="img-artwork vert-move " src="https://res.cloudinary.com/doem0zjpf/image/upload/v1562846054/jeees_aayrrr.png" alt="">
    </div>
